videos.description: Barry Brown Jr. comes away with a steal and throws down a fast-break dunk for Kansas State's first points against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Brown throws it down for KSU's first points of the game

videos.description: Kamau Stokes shows off his handle and finishes with a nice lay-in at the rim for Kansas State.
videos.headline: Stokes gets by a defender for a tough finish around the rim
